Package: GeneNeighborhood
Type: Package
Title: Analyze the Neighborhood (Upstream/Downstream Neighbors) of Genes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pascal GP Martin
Maintainer: Pascal GP Martin <pgp.martin@gmail.com>
Description: Extract and analyze the orientation and the proximity of upstream/downstream genes.
    Summaries, statistics and plots allow to analyze pre-defined groups of genes and compare them to a reference.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
